    • isOpposite

      public abstract boolean isOpposite(ActionDirection direction)
      Checks if the given direction is the opposite of this direction. This also includes that the opposite of UP is DOWN and vice versa. It also includes diagonals, so NORTH_EAST is the opposite of SOUTH_WEST, but also the opposite of SOUTH and WEST.
      Parameters:
      direction - The direction to check
      Returns:
      If the given direction is the opposite of this direction
